---
title: Crispy Chicken and Miso Double Shrimp with Veggie-Tossed Rice
description: We've got the ultimate crispy chicken stir-fry  filled to the brim with veggies for tonight's dinner! You also get the double the proteins with  juicy miso shrimp for perfect packed plate!
